</p></section><section id="GUID-0A01212B-8B5D-49AC-BC1D-38CB7A301CC0" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Function</title><p class="- topic/p "> Specifies how the engine should prevent condensation on the printheads when not operational. 
